  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/9fbc83f6a9166b578ca7098504b794ca.avif?t=1689161550\" width=307 height=307 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to undeveloped new lands, settler!</strong></h2>Here you have to survive in the difficult conditions of unknown lands!<br>Be careful, because it is full of mysteries and unfriendly robots. Solve the mystery of these robots and protect your people and your settlement!<br>Here's what you'll be doing:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/c628e1d0c31ad9396ed61b78968beb1a.poster.avif?t=1689161550\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/c628e1d0c31ad9396ed61b78968beb1a.webm?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/c628e1d0c31ad9396ed61b78968beb1a.mp4?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Mining. </i></strong><br>Over 50 types of resources required to craft all your equipment, weapons and buildings. Mine, store and explore new lands!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/efde5e76ef7c6db56c85d2a0f1bc03a0.poster.avif?t=1689161550\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/efde5e76ef7c6db56c85d2a0f1bc03a0.webm?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/efde5e76ef7c6db56c85d2a0f1bc03a0.mp4?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Dungeons with robots and bosses.</i></strong><br>Explore dungeons, solve puzzles and get valuable resources and rewards! For each cleared dungeon, you will receive a valuable part with which you can create your own robot and send it to extract resources!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/0b107ad9b8d510b9b7ccac262af69651.poster.avif?t=1689161550\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/0b107ad9b8d510b9b7ccac262af69651.webm?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/0b107ad9b8d510b9b7ccac262af69651.mp4?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Build!</i></strong><br>You can build your own house however you want, anywhere on the map! But do not forget that you will have to build houses for all the survivors and help them!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/f9e846786a4689ed0e277e5b030ae745.poster.avif?t=1689161550\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/f9e846786a4689ed0e277e5b030ae745.webm?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/f9e846786a4689ed0e277e5b030ae745.mp4?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Grow plants!</i></strong><br>Grow rare flowers and plants, with their help you can cook recipes and food that will help you!<br>You will get bonuses to hp, experience and much more!<br><strong><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Write yor own odyssey, Settler!</h2></i></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/7e079b0d813d461eb8d60cd34e2b936c.avif?t=1689161550\" width=512 height=468 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/9fbc83f6a9166b578ca7098504b794ca.avif?t=1689161550\" width=307 height=307 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to undeveloped new lands, settler!</strong></h2>Here you have to survive in the difficult conditions of unknown lands!<br>Be careful, because it is full of mysteries and unfriendly robots. Solve the mystery of these robots and protect your people and your settlement!<br>Here's what you'll be doing:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/c628e1d0c31ad9396ed61b78968beb1a.poster.avif?t=1689161550\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/c628e1d0c31ad9396ed61b78968beb1a.webm?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/c628e1d0c31ad9396ed61b78968beb1a.mp4?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Mining. </i></strong><br>Over 50 types of resources required to craft all your equipment, weapons and buildings. Mine, store and explore new lands!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/efde5e76ef7c6db56c85d2a0f1bc03a0.poster.avif?t=1689161550\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/efde5e76ef7c6db56c85d2a0f1bc03a0.webm?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/efde5e76ef7c6db56c85d2a0f1bc03a0.mp4?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Dungeons with robots and bosses.</i></strong><br>Explore dungeons, solve puzzles and get valuable resources and rewards! For each cleared dungeon, you will receive a valuable part with which you can create your own robot and send it to extract resources!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/0b107ad9b8d510b9b7ccac262af69651.poster.avif?t=1689161550\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/0b107ad9b8d510b9b7ccac262af69651.webm?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/0b107ad9b8d510b9b7ccac262af69651.mp4?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Build!</i></strong><br>You can build your own house however you want, anywhere on the map! But do not forget that you will have to build houses for all the survivors and help them!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/f9e846786a4689ed0e277e5b030ae745.poster.avif?t=1689161550\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/f9e846786a4689ed0e277e5b030ae745.webm?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/f9e846786a4689ed0e277e5b030ae745.mp4?t=1689161550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>Grow plants!</i></strong><br>Grow rare flowers and plants, with their help you can cook recipes and food that will help you!<br>You will get bonuses to hp, experience and much more!<br><strong><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Write yor own odyssey, Settler!</h2></i></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453390/extras/7e079b0d813d461eb8d60cd34e2b936c.avif?t=1689161550\" width=512 height=468 /></span>",
